Privacy Policy for Magic cards

This privacy policy applies to the Magic Cards app for mobile devices that was created by Mom & Child (hereby referred to as "We") as a free service. This service is intended for use "AS IS".

We are not interested in collecting any personal information. We believe such information is yours and yours alone. 
We do not store or transmit your personal details, nor do we include any advertising or analytics software that talks to third parties.

What Information Do We Collect?
We do not collect any personal information or connect to the internet. 

Contact
If you have any questions or concerns, please feel free to contact us via email at mom.and.kid.app@gmail.com.

If you installed this application from Google Play, then Google Play does collect some personal data. 
Please see the privacy policy for Google Play Services here: https://policies.google.com/privacy
